{"tid":226882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做乜都欠缺堅持同恒心","createTime":"2017-05-02T19:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T11:41:24.000Z","uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b76e33ecb8d6dfd61ba964d3e62003d0d59e4105","tid":226882,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:29:32.000Z","msg":"可以點改變?<br />\n小事至打機打波大至讀書工作<br />\n總係好易半途而慢慢頹(但又唔係完全放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1999有無巴明)<br />\n有無過來人分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且大個左至係咁<br />\n<br />\n背景: 在職廢青 仲有兩年30"},{"pid":"5cae3b7596c1b0191008dfcedbbde8eb6811bd7f","tid":226882,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f31ba148c584bd2e483e9fb64884cb389d5561d","tid":226882,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:36:33.000Z","msg":"調整心態<br />\n唔係無人幫到你"},{"pid":"69f2d4474698e14c1711b6dd18de18616e38cbd0","tid":226882,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:37:42.000Z","msg":"介紹你睇一本書<br />\n<br />\n叫拖延心理學<br />\n<br />\n好值得一睇"},{"pid":"e1f74bb8af01cf6d5c7c1b88e9a1793cdb975dde","tid":226882,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>介紹你睇一本書<br />\n<br />\n叫拖延心理學<br />\n<br />\n好值得一睇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正想睇番下書<br />\n無乜特別世藝 要補下修養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3102abbd2b743e8043df5b8b72cc968a303b7d7b","tid":226882,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:46:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>調整心態<br />\n唔係無人幫到你</blockquote><br />\n我都明<br />\n但有無d經驗分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42de23930d85c4f90503b932f22dd729c489cfb","tid":226882,"uid":41315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>介紹你睇一本書<br />\n<br />\n叫拖延心理學<br />\n<br />\n好值得一睇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正想睇番下書<br />\n無乜特別世藝 要補下修養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己就由中學開始<br />\n慢慢睇下睇下，睇左過百本書<br />\n屋企因此買左 2個新書櫃放書<br />\n<br />\n早排有個巴打又係希望自己有所進步<br />\n都俾我迫左佢睇左近10本書<br />\n<br />\n其實睇書唔一定係唯一既方法<br />\n但的確係提升自我既其中一種方法<br />\n想快既你亦可以睇 YouTube <br />\n不過我個人就鍾意書本既實在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望你都可以做得到<br />\n聽日，帶 100蚊，抽1個鐘<br />\n去最近既一間書局<br />\n去搵本你覺得岩自己既書，拎起就咁睇<br />\n唔岩就放低搵過本<br />\n不停咁打書釘，直到搵到一本書你係覺得你好興趣<br />\n好幫得到你既<br />\n<br />\n買左佢，放入你個袋<br />\n每日帶出去一有時間就睇<br />\n搭車 等lift 約左人遲到<br />\n放心唔會有人歧視你，係街睇書係好型好文青既一回事<br />\n直到睇哂成本書，再買下一本<br />\n<br />\n半年左右你會有好大改變"},{"pid":"b896798a9ab6f48308cbbd682bc4547eefd7bc3f","tid":226882,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>調整心態<br />\n唔係無人幫到你</blockquote><br />\n我都明<br />\n但有無d經驗分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我28歲前甚麼都不是<br />\n今年31, 事業有小成, <br />\n已是業界既精英, (絕唔係保險同金融<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果肙)<br />\n諗返除左努力, 根本無任何方法幫到你<br />\n你一日到黑諗住自己廢, 就只會廢落去<br />\n定啲目標俾自己, 慢慢完成佢"},{"pid":"402bf9b208654dd9002914fda1d5bc41d62e2a38","tid":226882,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:55:40.000Z","msg":"男人30真係關口位, <br />\n仲搵唔到自己條路"},{"pid":"6deb40843d8f115a1a41c5c84ed238d19ec9909f","tid":226882,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"